{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents25OUDSCheckboxIndeterminateV","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/init(selection:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/body"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/View-Implementations"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxindeterminate"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate/init(selection:accessibilityLabel:isError:)":{"fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"selection","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Binding","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI7BindingV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState","preciseIdentifier":"s:14OUDSComponents26OUDSCheckboxIndicatorStateO","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"accessibilityLabel","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isError","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxindeterminate\/init(selection:accessi